his! I'm ready.🚀\",\"option2\":\"This sounds complicated...🤔\",\"option3\":\"Just show me how it works!🎮\"},\"step2\":{\"explanation\":\"Don't worry - you've got this! See that post below? Someone's sharing something about climate change. Your job: decide if it's trustworthy or total nonsense.\",\"option1\":\"I can spot fake news already!\",\"option2\":\"Got it! Like the good stuff, call out the fake stuff.\",\"option3\":\"Wait, how do I know what's real?\"},\"step3\":{\"tips\":\"Exactly! Here's the secret: Look for exaggerated language, missing sources, and stuff that seems TOO crazy to be true. Try the first post - I'll tell you how you did!\",\"option1\":\"Okay, entering the feed now!\",\"option2\":\"Show me an example first?\"},\"example\":{\"message\":\"Here's an example post with explanations. Notice the exaggerated language and missing sources - these are red flags!\"},\"completed\":{\"message\":\"Game begins! You're all set to navigate the feed and identify misinformation. Good luck! 🎮\"}}},\"prebunking\":{\"modalLabel\":\"Prebunking information modal\",\"header\":{\"holdOn\":\"Hold on!\",\"misleading\":\"That's misleading!\"},\"body\":{\"techniquePrefix\":\"This post is using\",\"context\":\"Weather is not the same as Climate. Don't let isolated incidents distract from long-term data in the World Disasters Report.\",\"dataLink\":\"See the IFRC data on increasing heatwave trends.\"},\"continueButton\":\"Got it! Continue\"},\"errors\":{\"404\":{\"title\":\"Page Not Found\",\"description\":\"The page you are looking for does not exist.\",\"backHome\":\"Back to Home\"},\"500\":{\"title\":\"Server Error\",\"description\":\"Something went wrong on our end. Please try again later.\",\"reload\":\"Reload\"}}},\"timeZone\":\"Australia/Melbourne\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"header\",null,{\"className\":\"fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 h-14 bg-white\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flex h-full items-center justify-center md:justify-between md:px-6\",\"c